 MakeTreeView←{
 ⍝ ⍵ ←→ ref to explorer subform
 ⍝ ⍺ ←→ config settings
     f←⍵.##
     connections←f ListDatabases ⍺
     tree←⍎'tree'⍵.⎕WC'TreeView'('Size' 100 100)('Posn' 0 0)('Attach' 'Top' 'Left' 'Bottom' 'Right')
     depths←(≢connections)⍴0
     tree.Items←connections
     tree.Depth←depths
